{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "百物語", "storyInfo": "由於萌萌香在拍節目時無意拾起的一截斷刀，三船下令追捕萌萌香。澪試圖為她求情，但三船的手下還是追到了神社外面。在那位沉穩神職的掩護下，星熊和萌萌香成功逃脫。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交待你辦的事怎麼樣了？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議員大人終於同意金石集團和金石會的剝離了。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要您現在接下會長的位置，金石會就可以和金石集團徹底分離。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，那不如就把繼位儀式和明晚的花火大會同時辦了，你覺得怎麼樣？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵齋那邊的態度沒變，現在甚至多了星熊作為助力，我們真的能在一天之內……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的眉頭微微跳了一下。我知道你在想什麼。你知道我不會用這種事開玩笑，卻又對我沒信心。歸根究柢……", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "覺得我沒必要讓你模仿老東西的筆跡，把星熊叫回來徒增麻煩，是嗎？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十多年前，星熊手裡那面盾引發了不少腥風血雨。畢竟是老東西的最後一作……澪，你去過他家嗎？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好幾年前了。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他家最多的是什麼？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電視。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，電視。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老傢伙是很迂腐，但他的嗅覺偶爾也很靈敏。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他知道金石會如果永遠那麼打打殺殺下去，總有一天會徹底完蛋。所以，他盯上了源石晶體元件。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觸類旁通，他家打造金屬的工坊很快變成了製作晶體元件的小工坊，然後一炮打響。從此以後老傢伙沒工夫打造他最喜歡的神兵利器了。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在晶體產業蒸蒸日上的時候，老傢伙忽然從光元一系的破落公家那裡買到了鑄盾的材料和工藝。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據說為了那些材料和工藝，他用了當時組裡將近一半的流動資金。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得，對當時的金石會來說，一面這麼有來頭，而且幾乎可以肯定是他最後一作的盾，代表著什麼？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……傳位。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連你都知道的事，老傢伙卻放著不管了。他就這樣拖著，拖著，一直拖到南院的第一屆議會都要開選了。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對你們這輩的人來說，你們早就習慣了議會。但對當時的我們來說，沒有人知道那是什麼。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始我們以為他們是要改官制，但那是他們幾年後才做的事。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們那時只聽說，“議員”會從平民中選出來。結果整個南院都轟動了起來……然後，那個姓惟任的倒楣鬼就跳了出來。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那位議員候選人？", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。他當時有一大堆政見，核心卻是要把我們金石會從鍛冶町趕出去。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他甚至找了一群烏合之眾，每天在我們鍛冶町外面吵吵嚷嚷，讓我們無法做生意。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老東西——不，不只是老東西，整個金石會一開始都沒把他當回事，直到他的人越來越多，越來越多。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……您決定除掉他。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。後面的事你也都知道了。那個議員候選人死了之後，金石會才領教了什麼叫做民意沸騰。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是在那之後，我才明白，儘管在四大家族面前，議員只是拿來裝點門面的花瓶……", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對我們這些人而言，議員的一句話、一點頭，往往就能決定我們的生和死。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……恕我直言，其實您可以直接告訴我，如果鐵齋會長不從，您在繼位儀式上需要般若。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實說，有時候你還蠻像鐵齋的。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，鐵齋騎在我頭上是一回事，像你這樣忠心耿耿、知無不言，那又是另一回事。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，金石集團和金石會剝離之後，我自然不能再當這個金石會的會長。除了你，會裡還有第二個能接班的人嗎？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我進入政界，有了自己的一方勢力的那一天，自然也不會虧待你和你的金石會。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船自顧自地開始大笑。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他眼前的女性仍然面無表情，不知道她究竟是習慣了如此，是不敢相信自己聽見了什麼，還是對遠大的未來無動於衷。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於現在，我們的第一要務，仍然是萌萌香。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道的實在太多了，而且還和那個情報販子扯上了關係。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她為了把佐野口的斷刀留在身上，甚至不惜跳窗逃跑，這代表著什麼，你還不明白嗎？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生——", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不忍心，而且願意對我說，這很好。我也可以答應你，讓她得礦石病的事可以再考慮一下。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，首先，你得把她抓回來。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何都要收回她手上那把斷刀的刀鐔。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其次，她這個藝人無論如何都不可能再繼續當下去了。未來她必須處在我們的嚴密掌控之下。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣你滿意了嗎？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝您的寬宏大量。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等你把她抓來，還是讓她謝謝你吧。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g7_jinja_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽緩緩升上頭頂。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管沒有其他訪客，但庭園中有了四個人和一個神明的身影，也就不再顯得那麼空曠安靜。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星拿出身上能寫字的所有東西讓萌萌香簽名，萌萌香被猛烈的攻勢嚇了一跳，但簽名的速度一點也不慢。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庭院另一邊，宮司懷裡抱著剛剛那位橫衝直撞的神明，正和星熊說著什麼。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛畢竟也是神明大人要玩遊戲，我身為神職，自然也只能旁觀，不好插手，還請星熊小姐見諒。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_bell"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己不是也看得很開心嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有嗎？", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得有。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠心誠意侍奉神明，自然會讓人心情愉悅。星熊小姐和萌萌香小姐剛剛不也一樣？", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#12$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是更關心祂為什麼半夜闖入我家。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼叫“半夜闖入”，把我說得好像是什麼危險分子。突然有人在兇宅裡收垃圾倒垃圾，還躺在那裡睡覺，如果是你，不會覺得奇怪嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就因為是兇宅？御機發生的命案那麼多，鍛冶町更不是什麼太平的地方，為什麼你偏偏去窺探我家？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為怪談啊。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你和怪談到底有沒有關係？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“跟事件一同出現”和“引發怪談的元兇”完完全全就是兩回事，好嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我自己就能引發怪談，那我為什麼還要辛辛苦苦地騎著獨輪車到處跑？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，你完全就是一個湊熱鬧的傢伙，卻被人誤當成了引發怪談的怪談？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不錯，你理解力很好。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟你說，當神明是一件看天吃飯的事情。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡號稱是結緣的神社，按理來說，大多數人這輩子都在和人打交道，應該沒有什麼比人和人之間的“緣分”更重要的，對吧？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時局穩定，人們就祈求現有的緣分長長久久；時局不穩，人們就祈求緣分幫自己渡過難關，或是結些新的緣分。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但近十幾年，來這裡的人越來越少，越來越少，少到現在，一天能有十幾個人來就很了不起了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神職大人，這是真的嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍微有一點誇張，不過這幾年這裡人氣不旺，也的確是事實。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些神純粹就是懶鬼，越沒人來越高興。我就不一樣了，沒有事情發生，我都快無聊死了好嗎——", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1905_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，懶鬼來了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懶鬼？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，已經走到你的腳邊了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊看向自己腳下，但那裡除了神社的石頭地面以外什麼都沒有。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，我們神社的招牌，給客人看看不行嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1905_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "懶散的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1905_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊伸手去腳邊摸索。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在神職的眼中，她的手已經與那位神明的身軀重合，但星熊仍然覺得自己什麼都沒有摸到。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們神社之所以會傳出結緣的名聲，就是因為這個傢伙。凡是他覺得最近在結緣上有好事發生的人，他就願意出現在人家面前。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是他覺得你最近沒有什麼緣分，甚至是有什麼緣分要斷絕，就絕對不會現身。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都這麼說了，他還不願意在你面前現身，看來你最近有緣分要斷了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事在人為。這樣的一面之詞，星熊小姐也不用全都當真。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼還扯自家神明的後腿？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總而言之，人無聊了就會追求一些有的沒的，神也一樣。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛好你消失之後，御機就開始怪談頻發，我為了消閒解悶去追一下怪談，這也沒什麼不對吧？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼不說話了？害怕自己最近有緣分要斷了？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不是這樣，只是沒想到，連神明也會追逐這種虛無縹緲的事情。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個傢伙！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，你不是森內要找的神明。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不是。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，可以請你跟我們過去一趟嗎？口說無憑，假如你能在他面前像跟我和萌萌香這樣聊幾句……", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宮司大人，幫幫忙，這個鬼要把你家的神明抓走欸！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾年我也受了森內君不少恩惠，至少一直都有關東煮可以吃。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#12$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呿。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，本神明心胸寬廣，去一趟就去一趟。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊，你和宮司大人聊好了嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多了。吉星呢？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還要回去看店，就先走了。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個小妹妹也去嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。加上一位怪談纏身的萌萌香相伴，這樣總算是請得動你了吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#11$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都說了跟你走，有誰相伴很重要嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話雖如此，神明仍然把獨輪車騎到萌萌香身邊，左聞聞右探探，一副興致勃勃的樣子。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小妹妹，你的節目我也看了不少。你是不是什麼受詛咒的體質？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這我哪知道啊！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我其實很怕怪談的，也很希望以後身邊平平安安，再也不發生什麼怪事。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？你就不好奇嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想做好自己的演藝事業。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然怪談相關的東西確實幫我增加了不少人氣，但我覺得……這樣其實不太……光明正大。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藝人就應該靠自己的努力帶給大家快樂，這才是對的。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在像你這麼想的人也不常見了。你還蠻有趣的嘛。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對、對了，我剛好想問您呢！昨天晚上，我家發生了很可怕的事情！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我家的電視突然開始自己播放我唱歌的片段，還把這個片段和電視台的警報混在一起……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，不知道為什麼……還放了一段很可怕的影片……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖嘖！影片內容是什麼？不明生物？命案現場？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都不是，是澪小姐……沒過多久，她真的來我家了……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不就是電視線路有問題嗎？我要找的怪談不是這種。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是這種？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你既然追逐怪談，不就該相信怪談都是人類所為的嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個人真不解風情。如果都是人類搞的鬼，那我還追什麼啊？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂怪談，就是無論如何都找不到原因的事件。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人類找不到事件的原因，像森內那樣的傢伙，就怪到我們神明頭上。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而連神明都不知道原因的事件，那當然是因為有更加強大、更加神秘莫測、更加讓我興奮的東西，在我們背後搗亂啊。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，獨輪車確實是你騎的吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，一件小事而已，不要插嘴！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這麼說，你也在追逐神明嗎？追逐“神明”頭上的“神明”？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是如此！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是吉星？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們交換了終端號碼？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。事務所很少給我與粉絲直接交流的機會，她又那麼熱情。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂？吉星？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是真的！我沒有這個意思——這不是我的意思！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對！我從來沒有說過要隱退！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，嗯。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……先不聊了？可能有人一直在跟著你？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！我現在就……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連神社也？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我立刻告訴大家！你也一定要小心！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#12$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ringoff"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人放出你要隱退的消息？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星說論壇上面傳得很厲害，不像是隨便哪個人亂說的，像是金石台放出的風聲……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星又是怎麼回事？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有金石會的人跟蹤她。她還說神社周圍可能也不安全，她出神門的時候看見有人在附近鬼鬼祟祟的。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次見到吉星的時候，幫我向她道個謝。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過也不用太過擔心啦。哪怕是橫行御機的黑道，若是敢滋擾神社境內，也只不過是自討苦吃。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果各位需要在神社境內暫避，可以進入室內，其餘事情由我應對。如果各位要離開，也可以按我指示走小路離開。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是趕快回去比較好。我們晚走一刻，他能在附近布下的人也就越多。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香，騎車就拜託你了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！騎了一整晚的車，我覺得自己現在也有一些心得了！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，宮司大人，我們就先走了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我跟你們走，是不是也能被那些黑道啊什麼的追著跑？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會儘量不引人注意——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就由我來出風頭囉？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出風頭是指——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是要幫我們引開黑道，對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從結果上講是這樣沒錯啦。偶爾戲耍一下那些呆頭呆腦的黑道，雖然比不上追逐怪談，但也算是消遣。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先從正門衝出去，吸引一下那些呆頭黑道的注意力，你們趁機從後面撤退，在森內那個笨蛋的攤子集合！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_fast_lp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "350,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等任何人回答，獨輪車便風馳電掣地駛向神門之外，踏板飛轉到大白天都只能看見殘影。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來神明很喜歡你們啊。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#2$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過現在不是感嘆的時候了。兩位請走這邊，我來為你們帶路。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好難找的小路……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話雖如此，也不敢說一定沒有人會發現這裡。兩位儘快離開吧。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝宮司大人鼎力相助。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼客氣——", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這邊有動靜！攝影師，快來快來，我覺得這邊可能有人！", "name": "記者的聲音"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片地也算是神社境內了，我們就這樣直接闖進來，是不是……", "name": "攝影師的聲音"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生的命令比較重要，還是神社的破規矩比較重要？快點過來！", "name": "記者的聲音"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用像那些混混一樣喊打喊殺，拿著麥克風和攝影機就能混口飯吃，還有比這個更好賺的工作嗎？過來！", "name": "記者的聲音"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宮司大人，現、現在怎麼辦？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神職閉口不言，臉上愉快隨和、偶爾甚至有些自得其樂的神色已然消失不見。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位暫且在這裡稍等一下。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……要出手了？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過是例行公事，祓除些許邪穢罷了。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#2$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windchime_JP", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宮司站定在原地，御幣隨手一揮，風鈴停擺，樹葉微顫。空氣驟然變得稀薄而澄淨。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$faceoff_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.05, "yScaleTo": 1.05, "duration": 1.9}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g7_jinja_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_OriginiumArts_llfather"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_OriginiumArts_llfather_lp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晶瑩的火自寬袍大袖間噴湧而出，像是凝固的清泉，並不奔騰，甚至沒有搖動，只是靜謐地飄浮在空中，直到風聲自神門的方向傳來。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是神明與人遊戲時絕不會掀起的、銳利如刀刃的惡風。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "望見後院處燃起的渺遠狐火，神門處的神明鬆開車把立起身，帶著一絲得意地揚起前爪，向空中一揮——"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firecut", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.5, "g": 0.5, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.1, "r": 0.5, "g": 0.5, "b": 0.8, "fadetime": 1.25, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晶瑩的火焰宛如驅邪的雷一般炸開，圍繞整個神社的注連繩瞬間燃起狐火，將現世與神域分隔。"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而酷烈的風在神域外圍爆發開來，竊聽器、無人機、攝影機，覆蓋在上面的偽裝全數被掀開，連機器本身也被吹到半空之中。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好大的風——設、設備怎麼飛起來了？！", "name": "攝影師的聲音"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "御幣劃破風的中軸，圍繞著神域肆意生長的狐火倏地分裂開來。風剝開那些設備的外殼，而火精準地穿過裸露出來的每一組核心。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被擊中的設備內部燃起絢麗卻無聲的白焰，一瞬之後，又紛紛炸裂、焦黑、炭化。"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宮司大人……難道是個隱藏的源石技藝大師？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一點小法術罷了，不足為奇。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間剛好。趁這個機會，兩位儘快出發吧。", "name": "沉穩的神職"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1902_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}